    "{\n",
    " \"cells\": [\n",
    "  {\"cell_type\":\"markdown\",\"metadata\":{},\"source\":[\"# Influencer Brand Mention Tracker\\n\",\"**NLP Project 75 of 100** — Extract products and brands from social media posts using NER.\"]},\n",
    "  {\"cell_type\":\"code\",\"execution_count\":null,\"metadata\":{},\"outputs\":[],\"source\":[\"import re, numpy as np, pandas as pd, matplotlib.pyplot as plt\\nimport warnings; warnings.filterwarnings('ignore')\\n%matplotlib inline\\nSEED = 42; rng = np.random.default_rng(SEED)\\nprint('Loaded.')\"]},\n",
    "  {\"cell_type\":\"code\",\"execution_count\":null,\"metadata\":{},\"outputs\":[],\"source\":[\"posts = [\\n    'Loving my new iPhone 15 Pro! The camera is insane 📸 #Apple',\\n    'Just switched to the Samsung Galaxy S25, way better than my old phone',\\n    'My Nike Air Max are the most comfortable shoes I own 👟',\\n    'Started using ChatGPT for work and it saves me hours every day',\\n    'Wearing my new Adidas Ultraboost for the marathon today 🏃',\\n    'The Tesla Model Y is perfect for road trips, autopilot is amazing',\\n    'Got the new MacBook Pro M4 and the performance is incredible',\\n    'Sephora has the best skincare deals right now, got my Fenty Beauty haul',\\n]\\n\\nBRANDS = ['Apple','iPhone','Samsung','Galaxy','Nike','Adidas','Tesla','MacBook',\\n          'ChatGPT','Sephora','Fenty','Google','Amazon','Spotify','Netflix']\\n\\ndef extract_brands(text):\\n    found = [b for b in BRANDS if b.lower() in text.lower()]\\n    hashtags = re.findall(r'#(\\\\w+)', text)\\n    return found, hashtags\\n\\nresults = []\\nfor post in posts:\\n    brands, tags = extract_brands(post)\\n    results.append({'post': post[:50], 'brands': brands, 'hashtags': tags})\\n    print(f'Post: {post[:60]}...')\\n    print(f'  Brands: {brands}, Tags: {tags}\\\\n')\\n\\n# Brand frequency\\nfrom collections import Counter\\nall_brands = [b for r in results for b in r['brands']]\\nbrand_counts = Counter(all_brands)\\nprint('Brand Frequency:', dict(brand_counts))\"]},\n",
    "  {\"cell_type\":\"code\",\"execution_count\":null,\"metadata\":{},\"outputs\":[],\"source\":[\"pd.Series(brand_counts).plot(kind='barh', color='steelblue', title='Brand Mentions')\\nplt.tight_layout(); plt.show()\"]},\n",
    "  {\"cell_type\":\"markdown\",\"metadata\":{},\"source\":[\"## Summary\\n\",\"- **Dictionary-based brand extraction is fast and precise.**\\n\",\"- **For production, use NER models** to catch brand mentions not in dictionary.\\n\",\"- **Track brand mentions over time** for trend analysis.\\n\",\"- **Combine with sentiment** to measure brand perception.\"]}\n",
